title: FANTOM Update: Raise $USDC and $DAI Collateral Cap
body:
Intro: This is a vote to raise the $USDC and $DAI collateral cap on FANTOM C.R.E.A.M. market.
Proposal: Listing Committee
Rational: Update and improve FANTOM market.

For: 
Raise Collateral Cap - USDC to $3M, DAI to $3M
Against: 
Do not make any changes to FANTOM market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
